Package FlightMachine

Class wwiiAirplane

java.lang.Object
Superclass.Vehicle
FlightMachine.Aircraft
FlightMachine.wwiiAirplane
public class wwiiAirplane
extends Aircraft
The wwiiAirplane class is designed to contain the most basic attributes/methods which any WWII Airplane should possess.
Author:
Kevin Courey
